data.description: NEW LOWER PRICE! Located in town but off the main street in Lineville, this home is within walking distance to post office, doctor's office, and other city conveniences. The 2 or 3 bedroom, 2 bath all brick home is on a half acre lot with city water, sewage and natural gas. The HVAC unit was replaced in 2016. Inside the home is a large living room with formal dining room; has hardwood floors throughout except for kitchen and bathrooms. One of the rooms is currently used as a den but could also be a 3rd bedroom, if needed. With a few cosmetic updates needed, this home would be move-in ready!
